{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act18d3_level_act18d3_01_beg","storyGroup":"act18d3","storySort":1,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"SV-1","storyName":"闯入者","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"深夜，斯卡蒂发现医疗舱里的幽灵鲨失踪，而掳走她的正是幽灵鲨以前的队长歌蕾蒂娅。临走之前，歌蕾蒂娅告诉斯卡蒂，接下来她们将前往一座伊比利亚小城。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act18d3/level_act18d3_01_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act18d3_01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"next":1,"characters":["罗德岛干员","斯卡蒂","？？？","歌蕾蒂娅","赏金猎人A","赏金猎人B","赏金猎人C"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"text","text":"沉默。怪异。捉摸不定。外乡人。","id":5},{"type":"text","text":"他们自然会这么说。","id":6},{"type":"text","text":"阴暗。冷血。见死不救。天生怪物。","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"所有人在背后都会这么说。","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"是啊。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"人只要失去了故乡，就什么都不是了。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"照理来说，来到这里的我，应该能开始一个新的生活。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"只是，过往挥之不去。这些东西会顺着影子爬上你的小腿，把你向泥沼深处拽去。","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"我们谁都摆脱不了过往。","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"如果有一天，你的故乡找上了你......","id":16},{"type":"dialog","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":18},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"stopmusic","id":20},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$farce_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_farce_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":25,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"2:33 A.M. 天气/阴","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"罗德岛本舰，走廊","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"好啦！等这份报告提交完成，你的外勤任务就算结束了。","id":32,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯。","id":34,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"等一下，又是......空白？咳，咳咳......","id":36,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"从头到尾，只有“完成”两个字啊！","id":37,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯？","id":39,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"任务确实完成了。","id":40,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"是、是这样没错......","id":42,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......你多写两句话也不会有什么问题吧？！","id":43,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯？","id":45,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（怎么办......比想象的还难对付？）","id":47,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（之前没和她说过什么话，这回说是要和她对接，虽然组长提醒过......但果然还是很难办。）","id":48,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（深呼吸）","id":49,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"好、好的，我明白了。","id":51,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"关于任务中的细节，如果博士有疑问，会再找你确认。","id":52,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#5","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......博士？","id":54,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#5","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"是的，凯尔希医生说你也许不会想向她提交报告......她还说阿米娅对你太温柔了，这样下去是不行的......之类。","id":56,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"然后就把这次任务归档到博士那边了。","id":57,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这个女人，哼。","id":59,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"那你想直接向博士面呈报告吗？现在博士好像不在，你可以休息几天，等博士回来。","id":61,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"现在你提交的这份报告，真的很需要再补充！","id":62,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#5","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":64,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"很麻烦。","id":65,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"那么，任务编码F1071，确认提交，后续补充——","id":67,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"等等。","id":69,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"咦？","id":71,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"把档案还给我。我想起来，再完善点内容也可以。","id":73,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#3","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"啊！当然可以！那就麻烦你啦。","id":75,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"（比预想的要顺利一些啊......）","id":76,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"这样的话，我这边没什么事了，还请回去好好休......嗯？","id":78,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialog","id":79},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":82,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"你的脸色一下子就变了，发生什么了？","id":84,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"可能是。","id":86,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"啊？在这里？船上吗？难道是入侵者？！听人说你五感特别敏锐，难道是......","id":88,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不对啊，如果船上有危险，警报会响起来吧？","id":89,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......歌声。","id":91,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"歌？什么歌？呃，很安静啊，我没听见......","id":93,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这里，为什么会有歌声？","id":95,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"确实好像有些嗡嗡声，但那也不是歌吧？罗德岛上的各类仪器都还在运转，有可能是，是机械振动？你还没太习惯吗？","id":97,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","name2":"char_263_skadi#8","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"不，气味。","id":99,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"海水的味道。","id":100,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":101},{"type":"character","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"char_016_medic","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"......斯卡蒂？你有点吓到我了。你在说什......","id":105,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialog","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"咦？喂！斯卡蒂！","id":108,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"dialog","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":111,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"background","id":113},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":114},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂跑得太急、太快，她跑进楼梯通道，她害怕乘电梯几秒间的焦虑就会让那气味溜走。","id":115},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一个猎人走上海岸♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":117},{"type":"subtitle","id":118},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":119},{"type":"text","text":"她能听到这歌。这艘船上的大多数人，他们听不见。","id":120},{"type":"text","text":"这种语言，这种旋律，唤起了她的回忆。她不是个恋旧的人，但她太熟悉了。","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"但......不该这样。这首歌不该出现在这里。","id":122},{"type":"dialog","id":123},{"type":"subtitle","text":"他的家乡在后，徒余哀叹♪","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":124},{"type":"subtitle","id":125},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"歌声在这艘船的管道里游移。","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"海水的气味从舱壁里不断渗出来。","id":128},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":130},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂也同样记得这味道。潮湿逼近了她，她的皮肤不住地收缩、绷紧。紧张，却也是激动。","id":131},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":133},{"type":"text","text":"难道她醒了？她不禁加快了脚步。","id":134},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"幽灵鲨！","id":136,"figure":"char_016_medic"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":137},{"type":"dialog","id":138},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":139},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#8","id":140},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/9d/Avg_bg_bg_ri_1.png","id":141},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":146},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":147},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":150},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","id":151},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她拉开医疗舱的门。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":152},{"type":"subtitle","text":"床铺是空的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":153},{"type":"subtitle","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":157,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"subtitle","text":"也有可能是清醒了以后想出去走走吧。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":161},{"type":"subtitle","id":162},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"等等......这是什么？","id":165,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":166},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她捡起那个东西，捏了捏。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":169},{"type":"subtitle","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......好像是她的东西。","id":173,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"subtitle","text":"幽灵鲨的金链被随便地丢在地上。或许是故意的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":177},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她很讨厌这东西吗？那她肯定是不喜欢现在自己的身份了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":178},{"type":"subtitle","text":"教会，至少海里教会的所有事，都不是好事。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":179},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但......不对劲。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":180},{"type":"subtitle","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":182},{"type":"subtitle","text":"外人。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":183},{"type":"subtitle","text":"不知为什么，斯卡蒂突然想起了这个词儿。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":184},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她意识到那其实不是幽灵鲨的气味。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":185},{"type":"subtitle","text":"比起以前的幽灵鲨，现在这气味太浓烈，又太冷酷。斯卡蒂怀疑自己只是被惊喜冲昏了头脑。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":186},{"type":"subtitle","id":187},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":188},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"就在这附近。你是谁？出来。","id":190,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"subtitle","text":"是深海猎人。但不是幽灵鲨。竟然还有其他活下来的深海猎人！","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":194},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但为什么在这里？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":195},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......幽灵鲨去哪了？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":196},{"type":"subtitle","id":197},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":200,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......无论你是谁或者你是什么。出来。","id":201,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":203},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":204},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":205},{"type":"dialog","id":206},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":207},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她得去追。有什么不对劲。她感到对方的确在附近。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":209},{"type":"subtitle","id":210},{"type":"dialog","id":211},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","id":212},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":213},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":216},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂冲出房门，一个身影在走廊深处一闪而过。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":217},{"type":"subtitle","text":"不......有两个人。歌声仍在，对方仍在低吟。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":218},{"type":"subtitle","text":"幽灵鲨。那个深海猎人带走了幽灵鲨。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":219},{"type":"subtitle","id":220},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","blackstart":"0.3","blackend":"0.5","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"真慢。","id":223,"figure":["avg_474_gladiia_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"再不过来，我们可就要走了。","id":224,"figure":["avg_474_gladiia_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"猎人！你是谁？","id":226,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂一跃，转过角落，她不自主地摸索起身上能用的武器。","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"——你在做什么？","id":229,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"那一刻她竟先直视了对方的双眼。","id":230},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......等等，你是......","id":232,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"一个自己没有想过的人。","id":233},{"type":"dialog","id":234},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":237},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":238,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":239},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","blackstart":"0.3","blackend":"0.5","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"斯卡蒂。","id":242,"figure":["avg_474_gladiia_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"气色不错。","id":243,"figure":["avg_474_gladiia_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......你......难道是二大队的，幽灵鲨的队长......？","id":245,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你是......歌蕾蒂娅......？！","id":246,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"有些时日了，斯卡蒂。你还能记起阿戈尔的歌，我很欣慰。","id":248,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":249},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂没能从她的表情里抠出哪怕一丝丝的“欣慰”。这个女人，从自己知道她开始，表情就从来没变过。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":252},{"type":"subtitle","text":"高挑的女性抱着幽灵鲨。数年来，斯卡蒂唯一知晓还存活的深海猎人，幽灵鲨，现在正靠在歌蕾蒂娅的肩上，做着又一场难得平静的梦。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":253},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在幽灵鲨的队长吐出第一个词的同时，歌声消失了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":254},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂一阵恍惚。从舷窗涌入、独属陆地的干燥的风拂过斯卡蒂略显干燥的面颊，她心想，这个猎人还活着，歌蕾蒂娅活着。斯卡蒂终于又找到了一个同类。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":255},{"type":"subtitle","text":"不对。是歌蕾蒂娅找到了她们。只是......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":256},{"type":"subtitle","id":257},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......我以为你死了。你们拼死让我们过去的。我以为你们全死了。","id":260,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"生命可贵。很高兴看到你也活着。","id":261,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"既然幽灵鲨还活着，我也常在想，你们二队是不是还能有其他人活下来......","id":262,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你是怎么找到这里的？幽灵鲨......她还是呆在病房比较好。","id":263,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":264,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂印象里最严厉的猎人之一，在这时选择了一言不发。","id":265},{"type":"text","text":"怀疑在斯卡蒂心里滋生。","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"她变了很多。她现在未必认识你，她的身体也还很虚弱。","id":267,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"虚弱？猎人不会虚弱。","id":268,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你来陆地上多久了？","id":269,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"地上的病，特殊的病，在掏空她的身体。这艘船上的人能稳定她的病情。","id":270,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这些年过来，她从来没清醒过。现在的幽灵鲨是另外一个人。我不知道是什么把她变成了这样。","id":271,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅没说话，微风吹过，歌蕾蒂娅的发丝随之飘荡，掩住了她的眼神。","id":272},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂意识到了问题所在。","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......歌蕾蒂娅。你就是歌蕾蒂娅，我不会认错人。但你要做什么？","id":274,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你想带她去哪？","id":275,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我以为猎人在陆地上是自由的。我是不是理解错了什么？","id":276,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"不，歌蕾蒂娅......她还睡着。她想不想走，你没问过她。","id":277,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你想从这带走她。","id":278,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你的这些新同僚，你似乎对他们青睐有加。他们对你是否也一样？你随手就能捏碎他们的脊梁，又怎么能不让他们感到恐惧？","id":279,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"陆地上的这些人对我们有敌意也正常，但这艘船上的不会。我遇到的不会。","id":280,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我还没能理解你放松警惕的原因。","id":281,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"不......这件事我不想他们掺和，问题也不在我身上，不在他们身上。","id":282,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"text","text":"问题在你。","id":283},{"type":"text","text":"斯卡蒂往前走了一步。","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你这么做是什么意思，你最好说明下。","id":285,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"猎人斯卡蒂。","id":286,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"——在陆地上我不用执政官的身份约束你。","id":287,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"唔......","id":288,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"可我也没有义务向你坦白。","id":289,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我只是认为，我应该让你知道，是我带走了她，我自己的队员。这就足够。","id":290,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":291,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"为什么？","id":292,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"今晚的你还不需要知道原因。","id":293,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"但是幽灵鲨她！","id":294,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"——（伊比利亚语）——","id":295,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown3","id":298},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":300},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在那个名字完整地传到斯卡蒂耳朵里之前，歌蕾蒂娅就已自舷窗滑进了舰外的月色，幽灵鲨瘫软的身体也随之一起消失了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":301},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂没有伸手去抓，她动都没动。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":302},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她清楚，歌蕾蒂娅想跑，自己是怎么都追不上的；但如果歌蕾蒂娅只是想跑，那就不会给自己留下讯息。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":303},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她在求助，或者她在诱骗自己。斯卡蒂将信将疑，又别无他法。至少她没命令自己去做什么，别去做什么。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":304},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“盐风城。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":305},{"type":"subtitle","text":"歌蕾蒂娅是这么说的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":306},{"type":"subtitle","text":"斯卡蒂她不得不去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":307},{"type":"subtitle","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"盐风城。","id":310,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......这重逢也太不感人了。","id":311,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":312},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":313},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":314},{"type":"character","id":315},{"type":"image","id":316},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/58/Avg_bg_bg_desert_1.png","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":318},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$farce_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_farce_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":320,"musicid":3},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":321},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","fadetime":"1.5","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......你们在这干什么？","id":325,"figure":["char_263_skadi",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"喂，她是斯卡蒂吧？","id":327,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"2","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"我是觉得她有点眼熟。和画像有点像。","id":329,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"......啊！哈哈，得来全不费工夫啊......","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"是斯卡蒂没错，我们蹲对地方了。","id":332,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯？","id":334,"figure":["char_263_skadi",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"2","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"喂，她真应了......而且你看她那把剑。她真的是斯卡蒂！","id":336,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"斯卡蒂，你还记得“上尉”吗？我们拿了他的钱，要给他报仇，要你的命！","id":338,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"2","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"你头壳坏了......你头壳坏了！我就说这是个馊主意！","id":340,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"我们不是说拿了他的钱骗骗人就好吗？！什么报仇啊，什么拿悬赏啊，怎么可能！","id":341,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"你想想那些传闻！真要是她，这趟活儿还能有我们一个子儿吗？命都要赔上！","id":342,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"我看咱们还是趁早散了吧！拿上你的破铜烂铁逃吧！","id":343,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"呸。","id":345,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"你自个儿爬回到你的烂床上抱着驮兽的尿喊妈妈去吧。一个长头发的年轻姑娘就叫你吓破了胆儿。想让老子无功而返，没门儿！","id":346,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"2","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人C","text":"说得对！就算她真的是斯卡蒂，就算斯卡蒂再怎么厉害，那她现在也只有一个人对不对？","id":348,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人C","text":"我们有一、二......呃，好多个！","id":349,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"可是那些厉害的赏金猎人不都烂在了地里？那时候，她也是一个人！","id":351,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人B","text":"你再想想，你每次说自己人多的时候，真的会有好事？","id":352,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"有谁看见了？要我说，那几个家伙，说不定是夜里喝高了进了同一个漂亮库兰塔的屋里。","id":354,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"结果人家从裤裆里掏出弩来一阵乱射，把大家的脑袋都给轰烂了。","id":355,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"传闻就是那么回事，要是不夸大些，那些抱着琴唱歌的，那什么吟游歌手，他们还能有饭吃？","id":356,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"什么一剑能劈开五十座山啊......老子还能一拳头打穿伦蒂尼姆呢！","id":357,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"听我说兄弟们！想吃饭的就跟我一块上！","id":359,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人A","text":"管她斯卡蒂活卡蒂的，咱搁这儿弄死，之后不怕人抢金子！加上其他人悬赏她脑袋的钱，下半辈子根本不用愁！","id":360,"figure":"avg_npc_007"},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#8","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"给你们个机会。现在跑还来得及，我没时间和你们折腾。","id":362,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_008","focus":"1","id":363},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":364},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$chasing_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_bat_chasing_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":365,"musicid":4},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人C","text":"上啊！干死她！","id":366,"figure":"avg_npc_008"},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","id":368},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"char_263_skadi#8","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"......","id":371,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"（阿戈尔语）烂掉的海草最粘人。","id":372,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"没想到，不会变的就只有劣质赏金猎人的麻烦劲。","id":373,"figure":["char_263_skadi",7]},{"type":"dialog","id":374},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":377},{"type":"character","id":378},{"type":"image","id":379}],"characters":["罗德岛干员","斯卡蒂","？？？","歌蕾蒂娅","赏金猎人A","赏金猎人B","赏金猎人C"]}